Name: Sector Six
About the game: Sector Six is a side-scrolling, sci-fi shooter with a silhouette aesthetic, procedural loot, extensive customization, and story missions. Features: Save the Universe: Enter the distant future and join a desperate fight to stop the Eight Machines from destroying everything. Build your spaceship: Customize the performance, appearance, and size of your spaceship, make it unstoppable by installing relics and activating set effects. Modular difficulty system: Make the game as difficult as you want it to be. Higher difficulty means better rewards! Master the ship combat: Learn enemy attack patterns to counter them, find the ability combinations that fit your playstyle, and obliterate everything that stands in your way with lasers and missiles. Let's talk! Got questions, suggestions, or need help with the game? Leave a comment and I'll do my best to reply. Developer's Discord Developer's Twitter
